About Isaiah Hicks

Born and raised in Saint Louis, Missouri, I graduated from Belleville West High School with a passion for helping people in need. My mission is to make life easier for those who are traveling whether for business, family, or relocation by providing safe, stylish, and convenient living spaces.

I'm friendly, outgoing, and easy to communicate with. My core values are rooted in faith and personal growth: God first, Family, Mental Health, and Growth within yourself.

Our Services

RoyalStaysLLC offers professional short-term and long-term corporate housing solutions. Whether you need a place for a few weeks or several months, we provide high-quality, fully furnished accommodations designed for comfort and convenience.
